---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";

import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";

import appScreenshot from "../../images/app-screenshot.png";
import rubyLogo from "../../images/ruby-logo.svg";
import railsLogo from "../../images/rails-logo.svg";
import postgresLogo from "../../images/postgresql-logo.svg";
import christoph from "../../images/christoph.png";
import fritz from "../../images/fritz.jpg";
import wolfgang from "../../images/wolfgang.jpg";
import clemens from "../../images/clemens.jpg";
---

<Layout>
  <div>
    <div class="-mt-8 mb-50 sm:mb-60">
      <div
        class="site-logo mb-16 flex items-center justify-start gap-1 sm:mb-30 sm:justify-start md:gap-3"
      >
        <svg
          class="h-18 md:h-24"
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          viewBox="0 0 40 40"
          stroke="url(#grad1)"
        >
          <!-- Square Brackets [ ] - happy eyes ^^ -->
          <defs>
            <linearGradient id="grad1" x1="0%" y1="50%" x2="20%" y2="0%">
              <stop
                offset="0%"
                style="stop-color:var(--color-rose-400);stop-opacity:1"></stop>
              <stop
                offset="100%"
                style="stop-color:var(--color-orange-400);stop-opacity:1"
              ></stop>
            </linearGradient>
          </defs>
          <g>
            <path
              d="M 10 4 L 4 4 L 4 36 L 10 36"
              fill="none"
              stroke-width="1.5"
              stroke-linecap="round"></path>
            <path
              d="M 30 4 L 36 4 L 36 36 L 30 36"
              fill="none"
              stroke-width="1.5"
              stroke-linecap="round"></path>
            <path
              d="M 10 24 Q 20 32 30 24"
              fill="none"
              stroke-width="1.5"
              stroke-linecap="round"></path>
            <path
              d="M 12 18 Q 14 15 16 18"
              stroke-width="1.5"
              stroke-linecap="round"
              fill="none"></path>
            <path
              d="M 24 18 Q 26 15 28 18"
              stroke-width="1.5"
              stroke-linecap="round"
              fill="none"></path>
          </g>
        </svg>
        <h1
          class="inline-block bg-linear-to-tr from-rose-600 via-rose-400 to-orange-300 bg-clip-text text-5xl font-light tracking-tight text-transparent md:text-6xl"
        >
          Mit Freuden
        </h1>
      </div>

      <div
        class="font-serif text-4xl/tight tracking-tight text-neutral-600 sm:text-right sm:text-5xl/tight"
      >
        <p>What brings joy to&nbsp;life?</p>
        <p>
          Easy: really,<span
            class="bg-linear-to-tr from-rose-600 via-rose-400 to-orange-300 bg-clip-text text-transparent"
          >
            <span class="italic">really</span> well-made software.</span
          >
        </p>
        <p class="mt-10 italic">We think so too.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="relative -z-50 mx-auto mb-10 lg:mb-20">
      <div
        class="-mx-4 overflow-hidden bg-linear-to-b from-orange-100/60 to-transparent px-6 py-12 sm:-mx-6 sm:px-10 sm:py-16 md:-mx-6 lg:-mx-8 lg:rounded-3xl lg:bg-linear-to-br lg:to-orange-100/80"
      >
        <div
          class="mx-auto grid max-w-2xl grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-16 sm:gap-y-20 lg:mx-0 lg:max-w-none lg:grid-cols-2 lg:items-center lg:gap-y-0"
        >
          <div class="lg:row-start-2 lg:max-w-md">
            <h2
              class="mb-3 bg-linear-to-tr from-rose-600 via-rose-400 to-orange-300 bg-clip-text font-serif text-4xl/tight tracking-tight text-transparent md:mb-5 md:text-5xl/tight"
            >
              Software that delights
            </h2>
            <p class="mb-3 font-sans text-lg/8 text-pretty text-neutral-600/90">
              What's the point of great technology if no one enjoys using it?
              Really good software doesn't just work—it should be a pleasure to
              use.
            </p>
            <p
              class="mb-18 font-sans text-lg/8 text-pretty text-neutral-600/90"
            >
              That's why we care about intuitive usability and design that's not
              just good-looking, but genuinely functional.
            </p>
            <a
              href="#demo"
              class="group text-lg font-semibold text-rose-400 transition-all duration-200 hover:text-rose-600"
              ><span class="">Try it yourself</span>
              <span aria-hidden="true">→</span></a
            >
          </div>
          <Image
            src={appScreenshot}
            alt="Screenshot of a web app that delights"
            width="2048"
            class="max-w-xl min-w-full rounded-xl shadow-xl ring-1 shadow-orange-800/10 ring-white/10 blur-sm lg:row-span-4 lg:w-5xl lg:max-w-none"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div
      class="mx-auto mb-32 max-w-2xl pt-24 lg:mx-0 lg:mb-48 lg:max-w-none"
      id="solutions"
    >
      <h2
        class="mb-3 font-serif text-4xl tracking-tight text-neutral-600 md:mb-5 md:text-5xl"
      >
        Complete solutions
      </h2>

      <p class="max-w-2xl font-sans text-lg/8 text-pretty text-neutral-600">
        We build <span
          class="bg-linear-to-tr from-rose-600 via-rose-400 to-orange-300 bg-clip-text font-bold text-transparent"
          >production-ready software</span
        > with you—from first idea to smooth launch.
      </p>

      <dl
        class="mx-auto mt-16 grid max-w-2xl grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-16 text-base/7 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:mx-0 lg:max-w-none lg:grid-cols-3"
      >
        <div>
          <dt class="font-semibold text-neutral-800">Web-based</dt>
          <dd class="mt-1 text-neutral-600">
            Our solutions are web-based and run on any platform. Desktop at the
            office, tablet on the go, or phone in the field.
          </dd>
        </div>
        <div>
          <dt class="font-semibold text-neutral-800">Native mobile apps</dt>
          <dd class="mt-1 text-neutral-600">
            Reach your users anywhere, without compromising on performance or
            usability.
          </dd>
        </div>
        <div>
          <dt class="font-semibold text-gray-800">Integrated</dt>
          <dd class="mt-1 text-neutral-600">
            We're experts at integrating with existing systems and third-party
            services. Good software plays well with others.
          </dd>
        </div>
        <div>
          <dt class="font-semibold text-neutral-800">Easy to use</dt>
          <dd class="mt-1 text-neutral-600">
            Intuitive software that works well and looks good. So you can hit
            the ground running.
          </dd>
        </div>
        <div>
          <dt class="font-semibold text-neutral-800">Adaptable</dt>
          <dd class="mt-1 text-neutral-600">
            Unexpected changes? Our software evolves with your business.
            Whatever comes your way.
          </dd>
        </div>
        <div>
          <dt class="font-semibold text-neutral-800">Scalable</dt>
          <dd class="mt-1 text-neutral-600">
            Your business is growing? Great—the software grows with it, without
            over-engineering or runaway cloud costs.
          </dd>
        </div>
      </dl>
    </div>

    <div class="mx-auto mb-32 max-w-2xl lg:mb-48 lg:max-w-none">
      <h3
        class="mb-3 font-serif text-3xl tracking-normal text-neutral-600 md:mb-5 md:text-4xl"
      >
        Future-proof through proven technology
      </h3>

      <p class="max-w-2xl font-sans text-lg/8 text-pretty">
        We rely on <span
          class="bg-linear-to-tr from-rose-600 via-rose-400 to-orange-300 bg-clip-text font-bold text-transparent"
          >battle-tested, future-proof technologies</span
        > that scale with your business. Our focus is B2B solutions—workflow automation,
        data visualization, complex logistics systems—software that stays in production
        for years. We deliver fast, secure, and scalable solutions, from startups
        to enterprise.
      </p>

      <div class="mx-auto mt-16">
        <div
          class="-mx-4 grid grid-cols-2 gap-0.5 overflow-hidden sm:-mx-6 md:-mx-6 md:grid-cols-3 lg:-mx-8 lg:rounded-3xl"
        >
          <div class="bg-orange-100/50 p-8 sm:p-10">
            <Image
              width="158"
              height="48"
              src={rubyLogo}
              alt="Ruby"
              class="max-h-12 w-full object-contain"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="bg-orange-100/50 p-6 sm:p-10">
            <Image
              width="158"
              height="48"
              src={railsLogo}
              alt="Ruby on Rails"
              class="max-h-12 w-full object-contain"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="bg-orange-100/50 p-6 sm:p-10">
            <Image
              width="158"
              height="48"
              src={postgresLogo}
              alt="PostgreSQL"
              class="max-h-12 w-full object-contain"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div
      class="mx-auto mb-16 max-w-2xl pt-24 lg:mx-0 lg:mb-30 lg:max-w-none"
      id="team"
    >
      <h2
        class="mb-3 font-serif text-4xl tracking-tight text-neutral-600 md:mb-5 md:text-5xl"
      >
        Together
      </h2>

      <p
        class="mb-3 max-w-2xl font-sans text-lg/8 text-pretty text-neutral-600"
      >
        For us, software development is more than writing code.
        <br />
        We <span
          class="bg-linear-to-tr from-rose-600 via-rose-400 to-orange-300 bg-clip-text font-bold text-transparent"
          >live your projects</span
        > with you, understand your goals, and build solutions that truly fit. No
        cookie-cutter packages, no half measures.
      </p>
      <p class="max-w-2xl font-sans text-lg/8 text-pretty text-neutral-600">
        Our team has delivered projects across industries—<span
          class="bg-linear-to-tr from-rose-600 via-rose-400 to-orange-300 bg-clip-text font-bold text-transparent"
          >from retail to energy to warehouse logistics</span
        >. Every industry has its challenges, and we know how to tackle them.
        The result: custom software that moves your business forward and brings
        joy to you and your team, every single day.
      </p>

      <ul
        role="list"
        class="mt-20 grid grid-cols-1 gap-y-20 md:grid-cols-2 md:gap-x-18 lg:mx-0 lg:max-w-none"
      >
        <li>
          <Image
            loading="lazy"
            src={clemens}
            alt=""
            class="aspect-square w-32 rounded-full object-cover outline-1 -outline-offset-1 outline-black/5"
            width="128"
          />
          <h3 class="mt-6 text-lg/8 font-semibold text-gray-900 sm:text-xl/8">
            Clemens Helm
          </h3>
          <!-- <p class="text-base/7 text-gray-600">TBD</p> -->
          <p class="mt-4 text-lg/8 text-pretty text-gray-600 lg:text-base/7">
            Clemens brings CTO and VP Engineering experience to helping teams
            rescue their Rails applications. With 20+ years in full-stack
            development, he focuses on performance optimization, security
            hardening, and long-term maintainability, turning legacy codebases
            into clean, reliable foundations that teams enjoy working with
            again.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <Image
            loading="lazy"
            src={christoph}
            alt=""
            class="aspect-square w-32 rounded-full object-cover outline-1 -outline-offset-1 outline-black/5"
            width="128"
          />
          <h3
            class="mt-6 text-lg/8 font-semibold text-neutral-900 sm:text-xl/8"
          >
            Christoph Lupprich
          </h3>
          <!-- <p class="text-base/7 text-neutral-600">TBD</p> -->
          <p class="mt-4 text-lg/8 text-pretty text-neutral-600 lg:text-base/7">
            With 15+ years building full-stack web applications, Christoph
            specializes in Ruby, Ruby on Rails, and PostgreSQL. From maritime
            safety systems to geospatial data processing, he's passionate about
            solving real business problems and bringing products to life from
            day one.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <Image
            loading="lazy"
            src={fritz}
            alt=""
            class="aspect-square w-32 rounded-full object-cover outline-1 -outline-offset-1 outline-black/5"
            width="128"
          />
          <h3
            class="mt-6 text-lg/8 font-semibold text-neutral-900 sm:text-xl/8"
          >
            Fritz Grabo
          </h3>
          <!-- <p class="text-base/7 text-neutral-600">TBD</p> -->
          <p class="mt-4 text-lg/8 text-pretty text-neutral-600 lg:text-base/7">
            Fritz brings 20+ years of experience in backend architecture and
            scaling web applications. He's mission-driven, focusing on
            meaningful problems while maintaining the balance between rapid
            development and robust infrastructure—from root servers to modern
            cloud solutions.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <Image
            loading="lazy"
            src={wolfgang}
            alt=""
            class="aspect-square w-32 rounded-full object-cover outline-1 -outline-offset-1 outline-black/5"
            width="128"
          />
          <h3
            class="mt-6 text-lg/8 font-semibold text-neutral-900 sm:text-xl/8"
          >
            Wolfgang Rittner
          </h3>
          <!-- <p class="text-base/7 text-neutral-600">TBD</p> -->
          <p class="mt-4 text-lg/8 text-pretty text-neutral-600 lg:text-base/7">
            A hands-on software architect with 20+ years under his belt,
            Wolfgang excels at cutting through complexity and delivering
            practical solutions. He jumps in to understand system interactions
            and provide actionable insights that unblock and accelerate
            projects.
          </p>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="mx-auto -mb-16 lg:mb-10">
      <div
        class="-mx-4 overflow-hidden bg-orange-100/50 px-6 pt-12 pb-24 sm:-mx-6 sm:px-10 sm:pt-16 sm:pb-32 md:-mx-6 lg:-mx-8 lg:rounded-3xl lg:pb-24"
      >
        <div
          class="mx-auto max-w-2xl lg:flex lg:max-w-7xl lg:items-center lg:justify-between"
        >
          <div>
            <h2
              class="bg-linear-to-tr from-rose-600 via-rose-400 to-orange-300 bg-clip-text font-serif text-4xl/tight tracking-tight text-transparent md:text-5xl/tight"
            >
              Sounds good?
            </h2>
            <p
              class="mb-6 max-w-2xl font-serif text-4xl/12 text-pretty text-neutral-600 md:max-w-3xl"
            >
              Then let's talk.
            </p>
            <p
              class="max-w-2xl font-serif text-4xl/12 text-pretty text-neutral-600 italic md:max-w-3xl"
            >
              We can't&nbsp;wait.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-10 flex items-center gap-x-6 lg:mt-0 lg:shrink-0">
            <a
              href="mailto:hello@mitfreuden.com"
              class="rounded-md bg-rose-500 px-3.5 py-2.5 text-lg font-semibold text-rose-50 shadow-xs hover:bg-rose-600 focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-indigo-600"
            >
              Say hello
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
